===Anime comics===
Various [[Film comic|anime comics]] have been released in [[Japan]] under [[Shueisha]]'s [[Jump Comics]] inprint, typically adapting the [[Naruto#Anime|''Naruto'']] and [[Naruto#Naruto: Shippuden|''Naruto Shippuden'']] theatrical films, though adaptations of the first ''Naruto'' [[original video animation|OVA]] and a [[List of Naruto: Shippuden episodes (season 6)|sixth season]] ''Naruto Shippuden'' TV special were also produced. [[Viz Media]] licensed and published the anime comic adaptations of the three ''Naruto'' films in North America in October 2007 and November 2008.

