===''Naruto Secret Chronicles'' series===

{{nihongo|'''''Naruto Secret Chronicles'''''|NARUTO -ナルト- 秘伝|Naruto Hiden"}} is a [[light novel]] series illustrated by [[Masashi Kishimoto]], which explores the stories of various characters after the conclusion of the original ''Naruto'' manga series. Announced in November 2014 alongside the final chapter of the manga, the series comprises six volumes, with the first released in February 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://j-books.shueisha.co.jp/pickup/naruto_hiden/|title=NARUTO -ナルト- 秘伝小説連続刊行中!!｜JUMP j BOOKS|publisher=[[Shueisha]]|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}</ref> [[Viz Media]] began publishing English translations of the novels in November 2015, starting with ''Naruto: Kakashi's Story''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://shonenjump.viz.com/blog/posts/more-naruto-books-are-coming|title=VIZ Blog / More Naruto Books are Coming!|publisher=[[Viz Media]]|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}</ref>
